        <p>₹6,000 yearly to small and marginal farmers.</p>
        <p>Eligibility: Farmers with up to 2 hectares land</p>
        <a href="https://pmkisan.gov.in/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"><button>Apply/Know More &nbsp; <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i></button></a>
    </div>
    <div class="vlog-content" style="text-align: center; background-color: #fce2d4;">
      <h3>Mahatma Gandhi National Rural Employment Guarantee Act (MGNREGA)</h3>
        <p>Provide 100 days of wage employment in rural areas.</p>
        <p>Eligibility: Any rural adult willing to do manual labor.</p>
        <a href="nrega.nic.in" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"><button>Apply/Know More &nbsp; <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i></button></a>
    </div>
