      <h3>Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala Yojana (PMUY)</h3>
        <p>Provide LPG gas connections to rural women.</p>
        <p>Eligibility: BPL households, SC/ST, PMAY, Antyodaya beneficiaries.</p>
        <a href="pmuy.gov.in" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"><button>Apply/Know More &nbsp; <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i></button></a>
    </div>
    <div class="vlog-content" style="text-align: center; background-color: #f2d9de;">
      <h3>Ayushman Bharat – PM Jan Arogya Yojana (PM-JAY)</h3>
        <p>₹5 lakh per family per year for hospitalisation(Free health insurance)</p>
        <p>Eligibility: Based on SECC 2011 data (no registration fee).</p>
        <a href="pmjay.gov.in" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"><button>Apply/Know More &nbsp; <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i></button></a>
